  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package targets W-AR-01: several credibility factors declare a requiredLevel but omit the structured acceptanceCriteria field, leaving the rationale for the required level undocumented. Decision is recorded as Accepted to exercise the weakener-detection system under a plausible-passing surface appearance.",
