      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on 6 input parameters. Sensitivity indices computed. However, blood viscosity model parameters and red blood cell fragility coefficients were fixed at nominal values without uncertainty characterization, limiting completeness of the UQ."
    },
    {
