    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required thresholds, the assessment team determined that the Monte Carlo UQ results provide sufficient confidence in the hemolysis predictions for regulatory submission purposes. Several factors lack formal acceptance criteria documentation; this was noted as a process gap but not treated as a blocking deficiency. Decision recorded as Accepted pending supplemental SQA and code verification activities in the next assessment cycle.",
